skdetail:

Invocation Name: fast counter
des:
Do you wanna go fast? You can use fast counter to have Alexa quickly count up to a certain number.

After you launch the skill, Alexa will ask you to provide your number. Alexa will quickly count up to your number.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
